00:00:12.904 --> 00:00:17.520
Hi! Welcome to Aha Emi Ruchi!

00:00:27.934 --> 00:00:33.458
What are you making?
Dosakaya Goru Chikkudukaya Kura

00:00:41.791 --> 00:00:44.565
Ingredients required to make Dosakaya Goru Chikkudukaya Kura

00:00:45.103 --> 00:00:56.411
Cucumber, Cluster Beans, Onions, Dry Red Chillies, Ginger-Garlic Paste,
 Tomato Paste, Coriander, Salt, Chilli Powder, Turmeric, Oil

00:01:14.969 --> 00:01:22.240
Heat a pan and add 2 tbsp of oil

00:01:33.756 --> 00:01:40.850
Add some chopped onions &amp; dry red chillies

00:01:47.709 --> 00:01:55.643
Add a pinch of turmeric powder and
1 tsp of ginger-garlic paste

00:02:08.390 --> 00:02:17.588
Add some chopped cluster beans and
some chopped cucumber

00:02:37.066 --> 00:02:40.525
Add salt as required

00:02:44.426 --> 00:02:50.585
Add 2 tsp of red chilli powder

00:03:00.546 --> 00:03:04.825
Add some chopped tomatoes

00:03:12.211 --> 00:03:18.475
Take the curry into a serving bowl
and garnish with some coriander

